499
00:27:39,554 --> 00:27:41,474
that relies on policing
and punishment,

500
00:27:41,554 --> 00:27:44,835
and investing in a community's
actual safety net,

501
00:27:44,955 --> 00:27:47,516
things like stable housing,
mental health services

502
00:27:47,636 --> 00:27:49,356
and community organizations.

503
00:27:49,436 --> 00:27:53,117
The concept is that the role
of the police can then shrink,

504
00:27:53,277 --> 00:27:55,597
because they are not
responding to the homeless,

505
00:27:55,677 --> 00:27:59,278
or to mental health calls,
or arresting children in schools,

506
00:27:59,358 --> 00:28:02,038
or really any other situation
where the best solution

507
00:28:02,118 --> 00:28:04,159
is not someone
showing up with a gun.

508
00:28:04,439 --> 00:28:07,359
That is the idea
behind "defund the police",

509
