the same analysis,"

571
00:31:33,876 --> 00:31:36,917
"the same recommendations
and the same inaction."

572
00:31:37,717 --> 00:31:41,358
We're in the same shit now
that we were in back then.

573
00:31:41,958 --> 00:31:44,318
And if you're not
directly impacted by it,

574
00:31:44,398 --> 00:31:47,719
it is tempting to look for a reason
